title: Teen Titans Season 1 [10-bit x264 AC3][576p]
description:
NOTE: THIS IS A 10-BIT ENCODE. These can be played using CCCP (cccp-project.net).

---

From the "Complete First Season" R1 NTSC DVDs (The Lost Episode is from the Tokyo DVD). High size/low CRF to avoid exacerbating the compression on the discs. Any aliasing/blocking/etc is most likely due to the source video. 576p because I think it benefits from a slight upscale.

---

Video: 10-bit x264 (766/768x576), ~1816-3019kbps
Audio: Untouched 2.0 AC3, 192kbps, English only
Subs: None

---

The other seasons will come as soon as I can get the DVDs. If you have complete ISOs for season 2, 4, or 5, let me know.
I won't be doing season 3 or the movie because those have great 8-bit HD versions which you can find here as well.


If you want English/French/Spanish subtitles, the French/Spanish dubs, or any of the special features, let me know and I'll upload those for you separately.
